sentences: Kaya Wilkins, better known as Okay Kaya, is a Norwegian-American musician and actress from New Jersey.
Wilkins' first release as Okay Kaya was the song "Damn, Gravity", which was released in 2015.
Wilkins released her first full-length album, Both, in 2018.
In 2020, Wilkins released her second full-length album under the moniker Okay Kaya titled Watch This Liquid Pour Itself in 2020 via Jagjaguwar.
In August 2020, Wilkins released her mixtape, Surviving is the New Living.
